45:30.405 --> 45:32.412
Come back in five days.

45:32.433 --> 45:36.428
What if I drop dead before then?
We'll cancel the appointment.

45:37.252 --> 45:38.476
Show me your tattoo.
Which one?

45:38.496 --> 45:41.346
You've got more than one?
Oh, joke.

45:42.472 --> 45:44.479
Like what you see?

